On the test, the Druid Epic loses it's snare component. That Is a big help for the druid epics because for the most part their ensare spell lasted a ton longer. 10 min vs 1min36seconds.... <br>
<br>
On the otherhand, Necro epics stay the same. In my humble opinion i believe the necro's would love to have just a 10 minute snare effect. Drop the damage for a long snare. This would appease the class more.<br>
<br>
Seems that both the epics were essentially the same, but druids got bumped up. <br>
<br>
